text: "Psycho" is a 2018 song by American rapper Post Malone featuring American singer Ty Dolla $ign and is the third single from his second studio album Beerbongs & Bentleys. It topped the single charts in Australia, Belgium, Canada, Slovakia, Sweden and the United States. It went to the top 10 in Austria, the Czech Republic, Denmark, Finland, Germany, Greece, Ireland, Malaysia, the Netherlands, New Zealand, Norway, Portugal and the United Kingdom. == References == Category:2018 songs Category:Post Malone songs Category:Ty Dolla Sign
